0.1.name: wordpress/noserub-for-wordpress
0.1.description:
If you have an account on a social network site powered by NoseRub, i.e. identoo.com this plugin provides a couple of widgets to show your lifestream your hCard, your contacts and, on newer installations of NoseRub, your services.

You can also choose to use your weblog as an OpenID-URL, powered by your NoseRub account.
